------- NAVIGATION ------- 

G + (Z,X,Y)           move
S + (Z,X,Y)           resize
R + (Z,X,Y)           rotate
RR                    rotate for all directions 
 
.                     center on selected object -- центрировать на выделенном объекте
Shift + S             3d cursor options
Alt + Z               transparency mode -- режим прозрачности
num -> '/'            local view


------- SELECT ------- 

A                     select all
alt + click           select around slice
L                     select object by point
Shift + S             3D cursor menu

H                     hide selected
Alt + H               unhide selected

Shift + Ctrl + "num+" select similar by selected style
  

------- EDIT ------- 

Shift + A             create something
Shift + R             repeat previous action
Shift + D             duplicate geometry
Alt + D               create linked copy (not a new instance)

GG                    move by edges

S + (Z,X,Y) + 0       vertex alignment (it is it ! )
E + (Z,X,Y)           extrude inner
E + S                 extrude outer
I                     inset faces
F                     create a polygon on open geometry, on selected faces -- создать полигон на открытой геометрии, по выделенным граням
V                     split geometry by selected edge
J                     split geometry (face) between some vertex (points)

p                     separate by
M                     merge -- соединить
Ctrl + R              add a cut section of points (scroll if you wan't more part's)
Ctrl + B              bevel (use C if owerlaps)
Ctrl + Shift + B      split a point
Ctrl + 'Num-'         boolean operation (addOn Bool Tool enablen (?))
Alt + V               extrude vertex and create faces by it


------- OTHER ------- 

F                     resize inner brush size
Shift + F             resize outer brush size

Ctrl + Shift + LCM    lasso mask (unedit)
Alt + M               clear mask


------- OTHER ------- 

Ctrl + T              Triangulate faces


------- BLENDER TOOLS TIPS ------- 
knife-bisect + fill + clear inner/outer (F - change knife direction)












